&lt;p&gt;And then -&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-r s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-r&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot;&gt;## Selecting Columns in an Given order&lt;/span&gt;
